We're police officers from the Dongjiang

20
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,910
Criminal Investigation Unit.

21
00:03:57,910 --> 00:03:58,590
I'm Zhou Mi,

22
00:03:58,270 --> 00:03:59,320
[Police]

23
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,810
and this is Wu Dong.

24
00:03:59,870 --> 00:04:00,590
We're here to ask you

25
00:04:00,590 --> 00:04:01,990
about some information.

26
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:06,030
When was the last time you saw

27
00:04:06,030 --> 00:04:07,030
your son-in-law,

28
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,800
Su Muxin?

29
00:04:08,830 --> 00:04:10,140
Last week.

30
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,080
In Dongjiang,

31
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,120
with Tong and Muxin,

32
00:04:14,150 --> 00:04:15,960
we had a meal together.

33
00:04:20,310 --> 00:04:21,510
From yesterday until today,

34
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:22,830
has Su Muxin contacted you

35
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:24,160
or your husband?

36
00:04:24,390 --> 00:04:25,000
No.

37
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,190
What's going on?

38
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:28,430
Why are you looking for Muxin?

39
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:31,800
Three months ago,

40
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,870
Qu Tong filed a report

41
00:04:32,870 --> 00:04:33,950
claiming her husband, Su Muxin

42
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:34,880
was abusing her.

43
00:04:35,120 --> 00:04:36,310
Is this true?

44
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,100
How embarrassing.

45
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:42,159
This matter is already behind us.

46
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,000
The young couple

47
00:04:44,830 --> 00:04:46,290
had a small disagreement.

48
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,850
It's all in the past,

49
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:50,720
isn't it, Tong?

50
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,290
It was all a misunderstanding.

51
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:06,680
Yes.

52
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:10,340
We had a big fight at that time.

53
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:13,640
In the heat of the moment,

54
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:16,040
I overreacted a bit.

55
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,920
I wasn't in a good mood then.

56
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,290
I was too impulsive.

57
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:27,780
How have I changed?

58
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,720
I feel quite embarrassed about it.

59
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,280
I'm so good to you.

60
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,070
Why don't you understand?

61
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:37,830
Looking back now, I really regret it.

62
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:42,950
Did Su Muxin ever

63
00:05:42,970 --> 00:05:43,890
abuse you?

64
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:50,510
No.

65
00:06:27,590 --> 00:06:29,050
What should I do?

66
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,280
What's wrong?

67
00:06:42,430 --> 00:06:43,760
Are you feeling unwell?

68
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,750
Qu Tong?

69
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,360
Yes.

70
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:52,020
My stomach doesn't feel well.

71
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:54,870
I heard that

72
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:57,159
you were in a sanatorium

73
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,180
for emotional issues.

74
00:06:59,430 --> 00:07:00,760
What emotional issues?

75
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,430
There's no basis for that at all.

76
00:07:03,430 --> 00:07:04,040
Is that so?

77
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:07,160
Qu Tong?

78
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:13,430
Yes.

79
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:15,510
It was just like

80
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,130
taking a vacation.

81
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:18,630
After your vacation,

82
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,070
how do you feel?

83
00:07:21,110 --> 00:07:22,210
Much better now.

84
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,490
So, after leaving the sanatorium,

85
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:26,590
you two have reconciled?

86
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,390
Yes.

87
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,530
[Zhuo'er Jewelry]

88
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:39,800
Hello, Mr. Fu.

89
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:43,390
Hello to both of you.

90
00:07:43,390 --> 00:07:44,920
Let me introduce myself...

91
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,310
I'm Fu Wenjiang.

92
00:07:46,390 --> 00:07:48,070
Mr. Fu is our company's second-in-command.

93
00:07:48,070 --> 00:07:49,600
All of Mr. Su's affairs

94
00:07:49,630 --> 00:07:51,360
are personally handled by him.

95
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,680
You're too kind.

96
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,810
Please, have a seat.

97
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,560
It's just an empty title,

98
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,870
just a position in name only.

99
00:07:58,190 --> 00:07:59,000
I'm just

100
00:07:59,190 --> 00:08:01,780
doing odd jobs for the company,

101
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:02,750
helping Muxin

102
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:04,280
share some of the workload.

103
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:07,630
You seem quite familiar with Su Muxin?

104
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:10,190
We were college classmates.

105
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:12,680
How's the relationship between Su Muxin

106
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:14,190
and his wife Qu Tong?

107
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:16,650
They were high school classmates.

108
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,630
They grew up together

109
00:08:17,630 --> 00:08:19,000
and are really close.

110
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,480
Here.

111
00:08:22,310 --> 00:08:23,040
Officers,

112
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:26,070
this is the room.

113
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,440
This...

114
00:08:32,549 --> 00:08:33,240
There are many

115
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:35,039
children's things here, right?

116
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,049
Mr. Su

117
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,720
previously had a daughter

118
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:39,480
who died in an accident.

119
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,960
Qu Tong couldn't handle it emotionally,

120
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:42,720
so

121
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:43,960
Muxin didn't want her

122
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,360
to be traumatized again.

123
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:50,490
Has Qu Tong recovered now?

124
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,930
She recovered long ago.

125
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:57,150
Let me ask you something:

126
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,360
when did you return to Yunzhou?

127
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,080
I wanted to visit you at noon

128
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:00,790
to ask you some questions,

129
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:02,270
but found you had already left,

130
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:03,930
so I made the trip for nothing.

131
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,960
I did leave at noon.

132
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,130
Where did you go?

133
00:09:08,390 --> 00:09:09,000
Home.

134
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:11,190
What time did you arrive?

135
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,600
Probably a bit earlier than you,

136
00:09:16,750 --> 00:09:17,750
around 4 o'clock.

137
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:21,910
It takes that long
to drive back to Yunzhou?

138
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,600
I didn't sleep well yesterday

139
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:24,730
and felt a bit dizzy.

140
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,690
So, after exiting the highway,

141
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:30,000
I went to the riverside
to rest for a while.

142
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:30,860
The riverside?

143
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:31,670
Yes.

144
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:44,040
Alright, you can stay here.

145
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:45,040
Let's go.

146
00:10:03,620 --> 00:10:08,980
