147
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:09,850
[Lunch, Dinner, Midnight Snacks, Fast Food
Welcome]

148
00:10:09,890 --> 00:10:12,590
[Xue's Blind Massage from Yunzhou]

149
00:10:16,070 --> 00:10:16,630
Mentor,

150
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,670
