288
00:18:55,830 --> 00:18:59,490
[Class 1, Senior 3]

289
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:00,270
Meili is in our class now.

290
00:19:00,270 --> 00:19:01,400
Please don't worry.

291
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,180
Thank you.

292
00:19:05,110 --> 00:19:06,840
Everyone, quiet down, please.

293
00:19:11,160 --> 00:19:11,960
I'd like to introduce

